items.name: Underarm Sweat Pads
items.description: 10 Pc Underarm Sweat Pads for Clothes
items.add_text: DRY UNDERARMS: These underarm sweat pads come with super absorption capacity which ensures that your underarms stay dry. SHIELDS & PROTECTS: Armpit sweat pads prolong the life of your clothes. STAY FRESH & HYDRATED - Its deodorizing nature keeps odour miles away from your underarms. BREATHABLE: The soft texture of the underarm sweat pads is breathable in nature and it is invisible from the outside of your clothes.
